{"tid":2211693,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修前真係要上呢個網睇睇，如果唔係好易出事!!!","createTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T18:04:50.000Z","uid":247471,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b6b7cf25b8f55d5a9e32f883e7cc24897c0827","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://angryblacklist.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fangryblacklist.blogspot.com%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZooRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=905d1994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://angryblacklist.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔睇隨時遇到黑店，間間都話得得得，做嗰時就錯錯錯...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e23c7ff700bb7bf47db0ce236d824786e54fa","tid":2211693,"uid":103647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"d post 無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af480891c34ad301d32cd46cb30631c58371f9c","tid":2211693,"uid":239912,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"見到巴打你咁 真係替你覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己都搞緊裝修 真係好撚煩<br />\n你仲要玩到爛尾⋯再搵人執手<br />\n難以想像咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bc796970ef74a7db33170c98419e3bc186a22b","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4af480891c34ad301d32cd46cb30631c58371f9c","tid":2211693,"uid":239912,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"見到巴打你咁 真係替你覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自己都搞緊裝修 真係好撚煩<br />\n你仲要玩到爛尾⋯再搵人執手<br />\n難以想像咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"係架，一錯就要重新做過，重要大失預算，酒店錢、存倉費全部自己嘔突，又無得告啲仆街黑店，重衰過自己搵師傅做(起碼平一半)，唔想有人再受害，睇住啲錢無啦啦一日一日咁比，屋又住唔到，傢俬電器要全部唔要得(係呀，全部要買過哂，因為比佢攪過啲線)，仲要冒住俾黑社會攪(玩你電話、攪你老人家、老婆等等)，所以年輕無病先好攪，有病分分鐘激L死自己或屋企人"},{"pid":"61e2de4b597a936d57c60c03054af911f42a0e93","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7f0e23c7ff700bb7bf47db0ce236d824786e54fa","tid":2211693,"uid":103647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"d post 無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:38:22.000Z","msg":"真係要個個睇，每間都衰唔同嘢，我後悔自己信咗廣告，如果唔係應該一早住得"},{"pid":"a155ddf710b19cbdda4aac3191e661356c56ba6e","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"a4b6b7cf25b8f55d5a9e32f883e7cc24897c0827","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:38:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://angryblacklist.blogspot.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fangryblacklist.blogspot.com%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZooRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=905d1994\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://angryblacklist.blogspot.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔睇隨時遇到黑店，間間都話得得得，做嗰時就錯錯錯...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"煩都要提多句比大家，千祈唔好信佢介紹比你嘅電器鋪或其他鋪頭，因為會打龍通，佢一遲起貨就會通知電器鋪或其他鋪頭夾期玩你，以制造你都無電器或其他嘢用住，我都係遲少少起貨啫你唔覺嘅去呃住你，我就係以為佢信得過所以領哂嘢，所有事都親力親為唔好信班裝修佬或設計公司，因為一定呃你唔識，一定唔可以信合約價，(VO)後加單先係重點，希望想裝修嘅你唔好再中我嘅伏，youtube facebook話好嘅全部都係假嘅，全部自己友扮客嚟嘅，祝大家好運"},{"pid":"c27