ail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBkfQVg.png&h=43aa4bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢樣能樣好出名，專係屯門搵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"平心而論啦<br />\n<br />\n2. 成日都有，係睇合唔合理<br />\n實在太多害群之馬，一開頭9up低價之後vo 重多過原價<br />\n<br />\n3. 龍頭係7咗無爭議，但爐位應該係造櫃之前要攞定俾廠開，21吋=535mm, 我通常做開550/600，應該都有爐啱裝<br />\n<br />\n4. 如果實呎係280，正常會預多10-20%損耗，式樣特別會再多啲，好難啱啱好<br />\n<br />\n其他未睇過就唔講啦"},{"pid":"fdc1d197a6c19f7a857f21c98132744fb7402758","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"我發現多咗人討論某幾間黑店，原來佢呃咗唔少人，有啲情況同我唔同添，大家裝修前真係要花少少時間望下"},{"pid":"9f7a7d0bce409336c469b44d836c5e21dfec63f0","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f0e23c7ff700bb7bf47db0ce236d824786e54fa","tid":2211693,"uid":103647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"d post 無時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"我見到有時間喎，由2019或之前"},{"pid":"3541ac1ab6fbe795b2776273d89e0c8b069a6197","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bc7ddf005045bbca1b080b7ade9081d6bf1b54a","tid":2211693,"uid":258907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:01:56.000Z","msg":"咁有冇白名單網..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"其實你幫襯前查下佢個名好啲，好多間都衰唔同嘢，總之唔好信啲平台，搵個好啲嘅師傅平一半有多"},{"pid":"c325d057ca6189b9011d8f896b4f33eb7b2807fb","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"15ff8e1f22235f754abb38fa59a1c7a176a33a26","tid":2211693,"uid":256127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:17:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oBkfQVg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoBkfQVg.png&h=43aa4bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢樣能樣好出名，專係屯門搵食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T12:24:06.000Z","msg":"佢度13個已經少，我總共收多咗40個制面，佢非孖蘇都當孖蘇計，直頭係搶，呢間比起我嗰單都算少問題，我水電門地下窗大門鐵閘無一幸免，家電全部比佢整爛哂要買過，電線又搏錯，買佢嘅電器又壞嘅要再買，地下牆都有空心磚要重做，廁所防水要重做，等於全屋重做..."},{"pid":"302eb0f75a8a98ebf488270bb60b43e65c9aeaee","tid":2211693,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"師兄幫你推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你太撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ffc59ea6fb72537ed999641f1afc37eba5437b","tid":2211693,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"強貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有埋白名單更好"},{"pid":"9150b93d2375e25407854ac8417770dfc8bd43f5","tid":2211693,"uid":277381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:08:04.000Z","msg":"仲以為係嗰啲裝修"},{"pid":"5d1692d818a2c41432f2a25ea991b6cc4debd8b4","tid":2211693,"uid":95059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"睇哂  好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c74a60ae29db7e20029672913d9c735301ddf46","tid":2211693,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62b9bd3522b376a95c52bdc1caacf67ee15e3b37","tid":2211693,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c74a60ae29db7e20029672913d9c735301ddf46","tid":2211693,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc7ddf005045bbca1b080b7ade9081d6bf1b54a","tid":2211693,"uid":258907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T23:01:56.000Z","msg":"咁有冇白名單網..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:32:04.000Z","msg":"我都想有"},{"pid":"1718f75e2ceada267a9a8f